# ZewedJobs Setup Guide

## Table of Contents
1. [System Requirements](#system-requirements)
2. [Quick Start](#quick-start)
3. [Detailed Setup](#detailed-setup)
4. [Configuration](#configuration)
5. [Testing](#testing)
6. [Troubleshooting](#troubleshooting)
7. [Next Steps](#next-steps)

## System Requirements

### Minimum Requirements
- **Operating System:** Ubuntu 20.04+, macOS 10.15+, Windows 10+
- **RAM:** 2GB minimum, 4GB recommended
- **Storage:** 2GB free space
- **Internet:** Broadband connection

### Software Requirements
- **Python:** 3.11 or higher
- **PHP:** 8.0 or higher
- **MySQL:** 8.0 or higher
- **Git:** Latest version
- **Composer:** (Optional) for PHP dependencies

### Development Tools (Optional)
- **Visual Studio Code** or any code editor
- **Postman** or **curl** for API testing
- **MySQL Workbench** or **phpMyAdmin**

## Quick Start

### One-Command Setup (Recommended)
```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/zewedjobs-complete.git
cd zewedjobs-complete

# Make the setup script executable
chmod +x RUN_ME_FIRST.sh

# Run the setup script
./RUN_ME_FIRST.sh
